FBIS4-63188 "drsov098_b_94028" FBIS-SOV-94-098 Daily Report 20 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Media Issues `Tsentr' TV Company To Start Broadcasting 21 May `Tsentr' TV Company To Start Broadcasting 21 May LD2005083094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0530 GMT 20 May 94 LD2005083094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] The "Tsentr" TV company starts broadcasting early on Saturday morning [May 21] on Ostankino's First Channel. This is the so called channel for late night viewers. It will start operating at 0145 hours [0945 GMT]. In the first broadcast you can watch the French film "The Snatch Squad." In the long-term, the organizers are planning various entertaining topics, together with reportage on the life of nocturnal Moscow.
